request.description:
**Minimal verify call.**

Passes just the customer's national number. Use this when you don't have biometric data — verification will return `MATCH` or `NO_MATCH` based on the backend's internal logic.

### Request body

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `nationalNumber` | string (≤32) | yes | The customer's national identification number. |
| `biometrics` | object | no | See the **Verify identity (with fingerprint)** request for the schema. |

### Headers automatically added

- `Authorization: Basic <base64(clientId:clientSecret)>` — handled by collection auth.
- `X-Request-Id: <uuid v7>` — generated by the pre-request script.

### Sample response (Hit-only plan)

```json
{
  "transaction": {
    "id": "019d6c81-50b4-7af7-bca0-52eb7016a852",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-08T09:51:47.580081Z",
    "status": "OK"
  },
  "result": {
    "transaction": {
      "id": "018e246e-17d1-7a6c-8e3b-9e48602b4742",
      "timestamp": "2026-01-01T12:00:00"
    },
    "verification": {
      "status": "MATCH",
      "biometric": {
        "status": true,
        "score": 92
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Sample response (Full-data plan)

Identical envelope, but `result.person` is populated:

```json
{
  "transaction": { /* ... */ },
  "result": {
    "transaction": { /* ... */ },
    "verification": { /* ... */ },
    "person": {
      "nationalNumber": "B123ADSBADADASDFCFDD",
      "demographics": {
        "names": {
          "arabic": { "first": "محمد", "last": "الحسني", "full": "محمد علي الحسني" },
          "latin":  { "first": "MOHAMMED", "last": "AL-HUSNI", "full": "MOHAMMED ALI AL-HUSNI" }
        },
        "phone": "+967700000000",
        "email": "mohammed@example.com",
        "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-01T00:00:00",
        "gender": { "id": "M", "text": "Male" }
      },
      "cards": [
        {
          "documentNumber": "ABC1234567",
          "type": "ID_CARD",
          "status": "ACTIVE",
          "expiry": "2030-01-01T23:59:59",
          "issue": "2020-01-01T00:00:00",
          "issuingAuthority": "MOI Yemen"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

